attributes.review: Guys, I got this app with the strict purpose of making sure that America stayed the safe and honest place that it should be with my man Donald Trump as leader! All of a sudden right after I downloaded the app my email shut down, my phone started glitching, etc. My electronics were on the fritz! How do I know that it was because of the app?! Me and an IT buddy of mine did a full diagnostic on my phone and computer and he informed me that the app made me susceptible to viruses, bugs, etc. So now I sit here with open technology and a heavy heart...if this app did that to my electronics imagine what another 4 years would do to this country.
